snippet.title: Object Ward - Official Visual Novel Trailer
snippet.description:
GAME RELEASING 5/31/24! Wishlist on Steam & itch! 

Itch: https://thugzilla.itch.io/object-ward 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1730500/Object_Ward/ 

Object Ward is a dark comedy/psychological drama about a man who sees everyone with inanimate objects for heads. What is real, and what is a hallucination? 

Features:
-6 love interests (4 men, 2 women)
-Over 40 CGs!
-21 Endings!
-A story you will never forget!

Furniture Voices- Podgekinn:  @podgekinn
